        "payload": "node.web.summary",
        "title": "Legend + Type Demo",
        "purpose": "This consumer graph imports a catalog via a bridge. The **Legend** tab is then able to list node classes (with meaning) and spawn them into the graph.\n\nGoal: make the Legend a real, deterministic creation surface (not a manual list).",
        "status": "active",
        "viewRole": "summary",
        "viewKind": "display",
        "exposedAuthority": "consume-view",
        "svg": "<svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 160\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\"><rect x=\"18\" y=\"18\" width=\"184\" height=\"124\" rx=\"18\" fill=\"#eff6ff\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"5\"/><path d=\"M52 62h116\" stroke=\"#111827\" stroke-width=\"10\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M52 98h72\" stroke=\"#111827\" stroke-width=\"10\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"98\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#2563eb\"/></svg>",
