    {
      "id": "legend-type-demo-instructions",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Instructions",
      "position": { "x": -260, "y": 40 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Try it\n\n1) Click the **Legend** tab (left side).\n2) You should see entries for the catalog node classes (ex: `summary-view`, `field`).\n3) Click the **+** icon next to an entry to spawn a node.\n\nIf the list is empty:\n- Ensure the bridge has `create` grant.\n- Ensure the catalog graph is reachable.\n\nThis graph is the consumer; the catalog graph is where the entries are declared."
      }
    },
